oster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824070/extras/462adc581e810e4054b41b79fc784864.poster.avif?t=1648078578\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824070/extras/462adc581e810e4054b41b79fc784864.webm?t=1648078578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824070/extras/462adc581e810e4054b41b79fc784864.mp4?t=1648078578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each level has a new combination of factors, monsters, and environment!",
